news.title: Flawed software affects Thiruvananthapuram corporation's property tax database
news.para: In some cases, buildings for which tax has been paid would be shown as demolished or non-existent, much to the shock of the taxpayers.

news.title: Tirupur civic body makes list of property tax defaulters public
news.para: The list is published on the city corporation’s official website. According to an official, some defaulters owe the civic body Rs13 lakh to Rs94 lakh in property tax, which they failed to pay up to the second quarter of the current financial year.

news.title: Over three lakh houses under PMAY-Gramin approved in Assam
news.para: "In the last one week, the Panchayat and Rural Development Department of Assam has been able to sanction 3,04,218 houses to the beneficiaries," he added.

news.title: Cidco cancels sale of disputed Nerul CRZ plot
news.para: Cidco informed the National Green Tribunal (NGT), in its additional affidavit, that the auction was cancelled as the bidding offer received for the 25,139 square metre plot was far below the prevailing market rate.

news.title: West Bengal to take back unutilised leased-out land from industrialists
news.para: The cabinet also decided to reward those industrialists who have set up factories on leased-out land by converting their land-lease to "unconditional deed".

news.title: Societies in Ahmedabad approach original builders for redevelopment work
news.para: Decades-old developer groups like Bakeri, Synthesis and Ami Corporation have received some proposals for redevelopment from their old societies.

news.title: MahaRERA to issue notices to 18,000 developers for details update failure
news.para: The authority has issued 2,000 such notices till January 10 and would complete the process of issuing the rest of the notices in a month.

news.title: IFC leases 35,000 sq ft office space in Mumbai's BKC from Brookfield
news.para: The global institution that makes strategic investments and advisory interventions across India has leased the front-office space from an entity owned by the Brookfield Asset Management in the commercial tower Godrej BKC.

news.title: New schemes for cancelled plots by Greater Noida authority
news.para: CEO Ritu Maheshwari conducted a meeting of all department heads on Tuesday to review the progress made against the defaulters, who are yet to clear their dues.

news.title: CBI books former CMD of Amrapali Group in eight-year-old murder case
news.para: In accordance with its procedures, the Central Bureau of Investigation (CBI) has taken over the probe into the FIR registered by the Lakhisarai police station in Bihar.

news.title: Trichy residents of peripheral ward complain of poor illumination, seek lights
news.para: Sri Mahalakshmi Nagar Residents’ Welfare Association said that four major residential settlements falling under ward 42 have 24 streetlight poles.

news.title: Buoyancy in real estate sector to stay fluid in 2023
news.para: The property market has witnessed an upswing in demand and price followed by the launch of fresh inventory in the market. The trend of market consolidation has led to an increased market share of organized branded players at key locations.

news.title: Construction to stop in towns under stress: Uttarakhand CM
news.para: ​CM Pushkar Singh Dhami told TOI on Tuesday that the carrying capacity would be a key part of the study and “any future (development) plan would be done on the basis of the survey findings”.

news.title: Kerala government to amend Land Assignment Act in upcoming assembly session
news.para: A Bill would be brought in the upcoming Assembly session beginning on January 23 to amend the Kerala Government Land Assignment Act, 1960. A high-level meeting, chaired by Chief Minister Pinarayi Vijayan, took a decision in this regard, according to a CMO statement.

news.title: Brick kilns back to work after penalty; Madras HC summons official
news.para: A special bench of Justice N Sathish Kumar and Justice D Bharatha Chakravarthy passed the interim order on a batch of pleas seeking closure and regulation of brick kilns located along the elephant corridors of Coimbatore.
